@startuml TVU-ITAM-Sequence-Login-Dashboard
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFF
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title TVU-ITAM - Sequence: Login + Load Dashboard\nLuồng xác thực và tải dữ liệu tổng quan

actor "User" as U
participant "Browser\n(index.html)" as Browser
participant "app.js\n(Router)" as Router
participant "api.js\n(Axios)" as APIClient
participant "Express\n(server.js)" as Express
participant "auth.js\n(Middleware)" as Auth
participant "authController.js" as AuthCtrl
participant "database\n(tvu_itam)" as DB
participant "dashboard.js\n(Frontend)" as Dashboard

U -> Browser : Mở http://localhost:5000
Browser -> Router : Khởi tạo SPA
Router -> Router : Kiểm tra localStorage\n{có token?}

alt Có token cũ
    Router -> APIClient : GET /api/auth/check\n(Authorization: Bearer <token>)
    APIClient -> Express : HTTP GET /api/auth/check
    Express -> Auth : authenticate()
    Auth -> DB : SELECT users WHERE id = ?
    DB --> Auth : {user, role, is_active}
    Auth --> Express : req.user
    Express -> AuthCtrl : check(req, res)
    
    alt Token hợp lệ
        AuthCtrl --> Express : {success: true, user: {...}}
        Express --> APIClient : 200 OK
        APIClient --> Router : {success: true}
        Router -> Router : currentUser = user\nnavigate to /dashboard
    else Token hết hạn / sai
        AuthCtrl --> Express : 401 Unauthorized
        Express --> APIClient : 401
        APIClient --> Router : {success: false}
        Router -> Router : Xóa token\nnavigate to /login
        Router -> Browser : Hiển thị Login Page
        U -> Browser : Nhập username & password
        Browser -> APIClient : POST /api/auth/login\n{username, password}
        APIClient -> Express : HTTP POST /api/auth/login
        Express -> AuthCtrl : login(req, res)
        AuthCtrl -> DB : SELECT users WHERE username = ?
        DB --> AuthCtrl : user row
        AuthCtrl -> AuthCtrl : So sánh password_hash\n(bcrypt.compare)
        
        alt Đăng nhập thành công
            AuthCtrl -> DB : INSERT INTO login_history\n(success=1)
            AuthCtrl -> AuthCtrl : Tạo JWT\n(24h expiration)
            AuthCtrl --> Express : {success: true,\ntoken, user}
            Express --> APIClient : 200 OK
            APIClient --> Browser : Lưu token\nlocalStorage
            APIClient --> Router : navigate('/dashboard')
        else Sai thông tin
            AuthCtrl -> DB : INSERT INTO login_history\n(success=0)
            AuthCtrl --> Express : 401 Invalid credentials
            Express --> APIClient : 401
            APIClient --> Browser : Toast.error()
        end
    end
end

' Dashboard flow
Router -> Dashboard : render()
Dashboard -> APIClient : GET /api/devices?limit=5\nGET /api/maintenance?limit=5\nGET /api/notifications\nGET /api/logs/login-history?limit=5
APIClient -> Express : HTTP GET (parallel)

Express -> Auth : authenticate() trên mỗi request
Auth --> Express : req.user = logged_in_user

Express -> DB : SELECT devices WHERE status='active' LIMIT 5
Express -> DB : SELECT maintenance WHERE status='cho_xu_ly' LIMIT 5
Express -> DB : SELECT COUNT(*) FROM maintenance_schedules\nWHERE status IN ('cho_xu_ly','da_duyet')\n  AND request_date < CURDATE()
Express -> DB : SELECT COUNT(*) FROM incident_reports\nWHERE status='open'
Express -> DB : SELECT ... FROM login_history LIMIT 5

DB --> Express : Kết quả truy vấn
Express --> Dashboard : 200 OK + JSON data

Dashboard -> Dashboard : Render stats cards\nRender charts (Chart.js)\nRender recent devices\nRender maintenance alerts\nRender activity log

note right of Dashboard
  Dashboard hiển thị:
  - Tổng số thiết bị (từ v_dashboard_stats)
  - Thiết bị đang bảo trì
  - Thiết bị hỏng
  - Bảo trì quá hạn
  - Sự có đang mở
  - Bảo trì sắp tới (7 ngày)
  - Thiết bị bảo hành sắp hết
  - Top thiết bị gần đây
  - Biểu đồ phân loại (Chart.js)
end note

U -> Browser : Xem Dashboard

@enduml
